showGraph creates a graph in the Atlas Graph View of the input

Parameters:
title - - the title to display in the graph view heading
roots - - the set of nodes that will be root nodes in the graph

omissions - - the set of nodes that will not be shown in the graph
highlights - - the set of nodes that will be highlighted in the graph
simplify - - the set of nodes whose relationships will be simplified in the graph (extra nodes will not be shown)
center - - the set of nodes that will be centered in the graph
